---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---

<div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300" id="use-cases">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-20 space-y-4 px-6 md:px-0">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
        Real-World Use Cases
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-8 space-y-8">

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <!-- <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy"> -->
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Document Authentication</h6>
            <!-- <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Mobile dev</p> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          As a notary platform, we needed a tamper-proof way to validate signed documents. With Tisura, our users can now prove the exact source of every file they receive — no more doubts, no more disputes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <!-- <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-1.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy"> -->
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">AI Content Verification</h6>
            <!-- <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Marketing</p> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          In our newsroom, we receive hundreds of media assets daily. Tisura lets our journalists verify the origin of AI-generated images and videos — ensuring nothing gets published without traceable authenticity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <!-- <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-2.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy"> -->
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">API Response Proof</h6>
            <!-- <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Developer</p> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          We provide critical financial data through APIs. With Tisura, our clients can now prove to auditors that specific data was fetched from our servers at a given time — zero room for manipulation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <!-- <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-3.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy"> -->
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">HR Document Integrity</h6>
            <!-- <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Mobile dev</p> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          We receive CVs and ID documents from candidates across the globe. With Tisura, we can now ensure those documents actually came from the applicant’s device — and haven’t been tampered with.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <!-- <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-4.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy"> -->
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Crypto Airdrop Fairness</h6>
            <!-- <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Manager</p> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          We used Tisura for our token airdrop campaign on Base. It let us prove eligibility was calculated fairly and that rewards came from verified logic — bringing real trust to our on-chain growth.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <!-- <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-2.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy"> -->
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Legal Dispute Evidence</h6>
            <!-- <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Mobile dev</p> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">
          When facing a contractual dispute, being able to prove that a file was sent — and came from the right source — can change everything. Tisura gave us that cryptographic edge in court.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
